                    <div class="detail-box" style="font-size: 18px;" >
                        <p class="padded-paragraph">
                            Seva Hands is a non-profit organization that was established in 2019. We are a group of four friends
                            driven by a common desire to make a positive impact on our community. Our journey began with the simple
                            goal of providing sandwiches to underprivileged students in local schools. However, the challenges posed
                            by the pandemic prompted us to rethink our objectives and expand our reach to create a more significant
                            and sustainable difference in the lives of the people we serve.
                             Today, Seva Hands has evolved from a service endeavor to the formation of a non-profit company called Seva
                            Hands Enterprise (SHE). Our commitment to our schools and the Sandwich Drive remains steadfast, but we have
                            also recognized the importance of empowering our community in more sustainable ways. We believe that by
                            enabling individuals to take care of themselves, we can create a stronger and more resilient society.
                        </p>
